------Who we are & What we do
Reach far
Fly high
Drink from the sky.
SKY DRINKER
What problems are we addressing?
People who like to go hiking or exploring often need to take a lot of water with them and sometimes may face the problems of water shortages or spend a lot of money buying bottled water.
Many countries and regions in the world are suffering from lack of water.
Some tourist spots are on the high mountains, which needed many people to carry water to the top of the mountain.
Sometimes traveling with ships can meet some unexpected happenings that will makes the time at sea longer, which might lead to shortage of freshwater.

Our goal
We hope to address problems in real life that are related to shortages of water. Our goal is to allow people to be free to do more things that they want to and live more comfortably with our products. We wish that in the future, everyone in the world gets freshwater to drink, and even people's choice of water source might change with our product.

Reach far, fly high, drink from the sky.
